          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Return a contiguous flattened array."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "A 1-D array, containing the elements of the input, is returned.  A copy is\nmade only if needed."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "As of NumPy 1.10, the returned array will have the same type as the input\narray. (for example, a masked array will be returned for a masked array\ninput)"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Extended Summary"
    },
